        "title": "How do you create and later access an application level resource?",
        "body": "<p>Edit: I am trying to create a shared database connection pool for all sessions of a web application. A different post said the best way to create a servlet context object was by having the init listener create it. I am however unclear on how to make this object available for use by my servlet.<\/p>\n",
